---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Equity Guardians is a first-of-its-kind foreclosure protection service focused exclusively on the financial interests of American homeowners."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Who we are"
    title="Passionate, dedicated, professional: we drive success into every homeowner's story."
    description="Equity Guardians is a state-of-the-art business model built to protect the single largest asset most Americans will ever own: the equity in their home."
  />

  <section>
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-copy reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our story</span>
        <h2>The safety net homeowners always deserved.</h2>
        <p class="lede">
          Every year, thousands of American homeowners lose their homes, and often the surplus
          equity within them, to foreclosure processes designed to protect lenders, not families.
          We started Equity Guardians to close that gap.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our team is built on a foundation of affiliated Realtors, who fund every client's
          protection out of their own commission and stay with the homeowner from purchase through
          any hardship that follows. On that foundation stands our cornerstone: a nationwide
          network of foreclosure-defense attorneys. Without them, none of this is possible. They
          are the ones who hold the line against servicers and courts, buy the homeowner time, and
          keep every legal option on the table. Around that structure we've assembled financial
          coaches and dedicated case managers, backed by technology that lets us deploy strategies
          and communications quickly so every hour of every professional on your file is spent on
          what matters. One mission ties it all together: use every resource we have (all of which
          leverage your equity) to prevent foreclosure at all costs. Only when a hardship is so
          severe that foreclosure truly cannot be avoided do we shift to our last resort: recover
          100% of your equity for you, at no cost to you, so you walk away with the financial
          relief you've earned and a place to land in a new rental home.
        </p>
        <p>
          If a sale ever becomes imminent, your Realtor is positioned to sell the home while your
          credit is still strong, and while your attorneys keep foreclosure at bay. Your Realtor
          then places you into the right rental in the meantime and helps you buy again once your
          financial footing is restored. Every member of the team works in coordination, always in
          the client's best interest.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="metrics reveal">
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-num">100+</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Attorneys nationwide</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-num">50</span>
          <span class="metric-label">States served</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-num">$0</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Cost to buyer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-num">2040</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Foreclosure-free vision</span>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading text-center reveal" style="margin-inline: auto;">
        <span class="eyebrow">What we believe</span>
        <h2>Three commitments to every homeowner we serve.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-3 mt-4">
        <div class="belief-card reveal">
          <div class="belief-num">01</div>
          <h3>Impactful Relationships</h3>
          <p>
            Every member is paired with a dedicated case manager who knows their file, timeline,
            and goals. No call queues. No re-explaining your situation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="belief-card reveal">
          <div class="belief-num">02</div>
          <h3>Experience You Can Verify</h3>
          <p>
            Our attorney network is vetted for foreclosure-defense expertise and jurisdictional
            fit, not by paid placement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="belief-card reveal">
          <div class="belief-num">03</div>
          <h3>Top-Rated Service</h3>
          <p>
            Coverage includes protection, savings, and recovery representation, free to the
            buyer through an affiliated Buyer's Realtor, for the life of the deed of trust.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band section-dark">
    <div class="container cta-inner">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="motto">SAVE · EARN · PROTECT</span>
        <h2>Ready to protect what you have already earned?</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent reveal">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--navy-950);
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }
  .metric {
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .metric-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--teal-400);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .metric-num small {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }
  .metric-label {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .belief-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }
  .belief-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
  .belief-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--teal-600);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .belief-card h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .belief-card p { color: var(--slate-600); font-size: 0.94rem; }

  .cta-band { padding-block: 4rem; }
  .cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta-inner h2 { max-width: 22ch; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
</style>
